du - estimate file space usage
-> displays the total amount of disk usage a filesystem is consuming
-> you can sort it amount accordingly
-> Useful for scenarios like filesystem houskeeping
Commonly used options:
1. du -sh * | grep 
2. du -sh * | sort -run

For hidden files:
du -hs * .[^.]*

